<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; 
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5; 
            color: #333; 
        }
        p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 40px; 
            font-size: 11px; 
            color: #999; 
        }
        a { color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hi,</p>
    <p>I hope you're doing well.</p>
    
    <p>{{ candidate_intro }}</p>

    <p>I’m currently exploring opportunities that align with my experience and would appreciate the chance to connect if there’s a potential fit.</p>

    {% set full_url = linkedin_id if (linkedin_id and 'linkedin.com' in linkedin_id) else (('https://www.linkedin.com/in/' + linkedin_id) if linkedin_id else '') %}
    {% if full_url %}
    <p>You can find more details on my background here: <a href="{{ full_url }}">{{ full_url }}</a></p>
    {% endif %}

    <p>Best,<br>
    {{ full_name }}<br>
    {{ candidate_email }}</p>

</body>
</html>
